OL,6,FMore than 7,000 potholes have been
OL,7,Freported across West Sussex since the
OL,8,Fbeginning of March.
OL,10,FThe county council said it's on course
OL,11,Fto have one of highest numbers of new
OL,12,Freports ever recorded in one month.
OL,14,FReports of defects this March have
OL,15,Falready reached almost 7,400.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the council said
OL,18,F4,500 of those were identified as
OL,19,Fneeding a repair and 3320 have been
OL,20,Fcompleted.
