OL,6,FThey said the weather had been a "big
OL,7,Fcontributing factor in potholes
OL,8,Fforming", "with February seeing the
OL,9,Fhighest level of rain since records
OL,10,Fbegan."
OL,12,F"Then in the first week of this month
OL,13,F(March), we experienced a month's
OL,14,Fworth of rain."
OL,16,F"In the past year, we have seen an
OL,17,Foverall record number of potholes and
OL,18,Fother safety defects being reported to
OL,19,Fus and we have also completed a record
OL,20,Fnumber of repairs."
