OL,6,FThe county council says it had
OL,7,Fapproved an additional #4 million to
OL,8,Fsupport highway maintenance activities
OL,9,Fand repairs in 2024/25.
OL,11,FIn Buckinghamshire, more than 32,000
OL,12,Froad repairs have been completed in
OL,13,Fthe past year.
OL,15,FThe council said more than 30 crews
OL,16,Fhave been working on road repairs,
OL,17,Fincluding potholes, some round the
OL,18,Fclock, seven days a week.
